+- The pair-selection entry is now sharpened with the theorem-stage verdict: the pair remains the least-tautological candidate, but its clean no-hidden-transfer route is closed because the later witness identity never sees the earlier slab -> incorporated into `factual/navier-stokes/exact-ns-delayed-transfer-precursor-pair.md` (UPDATE)
+- The event-side definition is also sharpened: the physical-space event survives intact, but its strongest same-family precursor continuation is now negative unless extra temporal-memory input is added -> incorporated into `factual/navier-stokes/exact-ns-physical-space-delayed-transfer-event.md` (UPDATE)
+
+### Findings extracted (meta — meta-exploration-003.md):
+
