+- **packetized-tao-circuit-noncanonical.md** — The packetized backup does not rescue the theorem program. Once packetization is introduced, the object depends on packet support, projection, leakage scalarization, and network-restoration conventions, so it is no longer one canonical exact-NS object. Packet canonization would still be a separate mission; later continuation instead bypassed packets entirely via the exact-NS physical-space flux/witness event. [CHECKED]
+- **exact-ns-physical-space-delayed-transfer-event.md** — The faithful physical-space exact-NS analogue of Tao's delayed handoff is a localized burst of positive forward interscale flux across one coarse-graining scale together with abrupt gain in a subscale band-energy witness after an earlier quiet interval. Filtering is observability, not reduced dynamics; Duchon-Robert is backup only; the clean no-hidden-transfer continuation on the selected same-family precursor is later closed negatively. [CHECKED]
+- **exact-ns-delayed-transfer-precursor-pair.md** — The preferred earlier-warning pair for the exact delayed-transfer event is cumulative positive `Pi_ell` mass on the disjoint predecessor slab of the same parabolic cylinder. It survives the tautology screen because it drops the later witness clause and stays on a fixed earlier interval; Duchon-Robert is backup only; later work shows the pair still lacks the exact backward-memory needed for an identity-only no-hidden-transfer theorem. [CHECKED]
+- **exact-ns-delayed-transfer-precursor-no-backward-memory.md** — The preferred delayed-transfer precursor pair fails structurally at the theorem stage: subtracting the filtered balances at `ell/rho` and `ell` controls only the final-window witness gain, boundary transport, and viscous band terms, while the earlier slab `R_-` never appears. So no theorem `P_flux^-(R_-) <= epsilon => E_flux impossible` follows from exact identities alone. [CHECKED]
 - **exact-ns-triadic-coefficient-rigidity.md** — Exact NS gives one Fourier-triad interaction law with geometry- and projector-fixed coefficients, not Tao's five independently engineered gate strengths. The live question is whether any exact support can realize Tao's full sign/size hierarchy inside that rigidity. [CHECKED]
 - **exact-ns-unavoidable-spectator-couplings.md** — Exact NS activates the full projected triad network plus mirror-mode bookkeeping, so Tao's desired channels do not come alone. After the definition gate, the stress test is exact: write the desired / internal-leakage / external-leakage ledger on a minimal helical support and see whether any adversarially favorable helicity choice can keep leakage genuinely subordinate. [CHECKED]
 
