 - **check-faithful-support-shrinkage-before-narrowing.md** — Before launching a follow-on mechanism mission that isolates one role or feature, ask whether the faithful exact support actually shrinks. If not, predecessor negatives may already settle the mission and the right verdict may already be a transferred model-level negative.
